{"tid":1362491,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"認真，請大家好好珍惜達哥。","createTime":"2019-07-25T01:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T12:44:00.000Z","uid":71632,"like":31,"dislike":197,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"fa632c162e2d94e591ad0cc24a1b0ad384f7ca5c","tid":1362491,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:35:01.000Z","msg":"試問依個香港有幾多個明星肯比你串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次達哥既出現 大家都唔係平日咁打氣<br />\n而係好似朋友互串大家咁大叫「卡關達」同「負碌」<br />\n個相處方式直情好似朋友一樣<br />\n<br />\n打fifa果陣既達哥真係可以當係收音機咁聽<br />\n有時仲可以學到唔少野 認識到唔同有趣既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打機果陣又介紹唔同game比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人中之龍都可能有一半係佢帶起<br />\n<br />\n但達哥依條撚屌都就30<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗諗下都睇左達哥3年 <br />\n達哥都總有一日會放棄做直播 佢始終有一日要拍拖結婚成家立室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請大家珍惜仲有達哥做直播既時間"},{"pid":"4a1479cd1e39b7ff5d93b217ae74df6b02414d9e","tid":1362491,"uid":128993,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"返大陸投共啦達狗"},{"pid":"99f17a99eb92d840106a954a53e1c8aecf3d2a85","tid":1362491,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:35:56.000Z","msg":"一出post就有7個負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcd4aeddbd3596f32d30e2c56356c7265704f9c","tid":1362491,"uid":118127,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:36:36.000Z","msg":"珍你老母咩"},{"pid":"ea282a456c2babed522a888ffc08805d88fc4101","tid":1362491,"uid":259700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:42:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"238adf64d665f48f89bf465de8a859031d61cf7a","tid":1362491,"uid":71632,"like":1,"dislike":5,"sc